Richard Mofe-Damijo RMD, the Johnnie Walker ambassador who was tagged as the whiskey connoisseur hosted friends and colleagues; Mo Abudu, Ayo Makun, Kate Henshaw, Omotola Jalade-Ekeinde, Don Jazzy, Chris Ubosi to the former Governor of Delta State, Emmanuel Uduaghan, Dele Momodu and more to an exclusive whisky dinner.  In his regular savvy classiness, he hosted them in an evening of delicacy at the swanky South Eatery & Social House in Victoria Island, Lagos. 